{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_10_02",
  "title": "奥山すみれ 2話 治さないとダメでしょ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "う……少し、ソファで寝ちゃってたみたいだな\nまだ仕事があるのに、居眠りなんてしてられな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… I think I fell asleep on the sofa for a bit.\nI still have work to do‚ I can't be napping…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　お腹にブランケットが掛かってる\n俺、いつの間に持ってきたんだ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? There's a blanket over my stomach.\nWhen did I bring this…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　ダメですよ、{user}さん！\n熱出して倒れてたんですから、じっとしてないと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! No‚ {user}-san!\nYou collapsed with a fever‚ so you need to stay still!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 143.78697089999903,
          "startTime": 20.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……すみれ？\nそういえば夢の中で、すみれの声を聞いたような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sumire?\nCome to think of it‚ I think I heard Sumire's voice in my dream…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "熱はどうですか？　少しは下がりましたか？\nあ、さっきより少し顔色は良くなってますね、良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How's your fever? Has it gone down a bit?\nOh‚ your complexion looks a bit better than earlier. That’s a relief.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.423381604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "額の冷却シート、取り替えましょうか\nちょっと待ってて下さいね、新しいのを持ってくるので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shall I change the cooling pad on your forehead?\nPlease wait a moment‚ I'll bring a new one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.9333353679,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6797.328190999999,
          "startTime": 52.2086660751
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "冷却シート？　……あ、ほんとだ\nもしかして、すみれが貼ってくれたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A cooling pad? …Oh‚ you're right.\nDid you put this on me‚ Sumire?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.2000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "はい。……もう、びっくりしたんですよ\n事務所に来たら、{user}さんが倒れてて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. …Come on‚ you scared me.\nWhen I came to the office‚ {user}-san had collapsed‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8000020345,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 61.8333353679
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "声掛けても返事しないし……さとみさんに連絡したら\n少し風邪っぽかったと言っていたので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and you weren't responding to my voice… When I contacted Satomi-san‚\nshe said you seemed a bit under the weather.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく毛布を持ってきて、寒くないようにして\n近くの薬屋さんで、冷却シートとかを買ってきたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I brought a blanket so you wouldn't get cold‚\nand I bought cooling sheets and such from a nearby pharmacy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.4000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "えーと、後は何をすればいいんだっけ\n看護師さんの本には、なんて書いてあったかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ what else should I do?\nWhat did the nursing book say…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.6000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "汗をかいたと思うので、着替えた方がいいんですけど\n{user}さんの着替えになりそうな服……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think you've been sweating‚ so you should change clothes‚\nbut clothes that might fit {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.7333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "私の服じゃ絶対入らないし\n身長が一番近いのは……franさん……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My clothes definitely won't fit‚\nand the closest in height would be… fran-san…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.5333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "す……すみれ、着替えはなくても大丈夫だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sumire‚ I don't need a change of clothes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.796394189,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（franさんに服なんか借りたら）\n（後でどうなることか……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If I borrowed clothes from fran-san‚）\n（who knows what might happen later…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.4666722616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか？　ならいいんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? If you say so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.3498217105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "後は解熱剤と……少しでも栄養のあるものを摂らないと\nスポーツドリンクは買ってきてあるんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next is fever reducer and… you need to eat something nutritious.\nI bought sports drinks‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.6666722616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば冷蔵庫にプリンがありました\nあれならつるっと喉を通りませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but I remember there was pudding in the refrigerator.\nWouldn't that go down your throat smoothly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そのくらいなら、なんとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can manage that much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.1995271523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "はい、あーんして下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here‚ please say \"ahh.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.1091053962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、すみれ。さすがに自分で食べられるから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ Sumire. I can eat by myself…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5459081728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ、病気の人に無理はさせられませんから\nそれに、いつも私がお世話になってるんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ I can’t let a sick person push themselves.\nBesides‚ you're always taking care of me‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.8999994915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "具合の悪い時くらい、私にもお世話させて下さい\nはい、あーん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so please let me take care of you when you're not feeling well.\nHere‚ say \"ahh.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.7666661581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こらこら、だから自分で食べられるって……\nあむ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-hey‚ I told you I can eat by myself…\nmunch…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.0333328248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、美味しそうですね。良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ you seem to like it. I'm glad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.0666049082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "これ、こころちゃんが、今日の収録後に食べるって\n楽しみにしてた、人気店のプリンなんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is pudding from a popular shop that Kokoro-chan\nwas looking forward to eating after today's recording.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.200005595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "げほっ、げほっ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "cough cough!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.7673079093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "あ、私が勝手にプリン持ってきたと思いました？\nさすがに人のおやつを盗ったりはしませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ did you think I brought the pudding without permission?\nI wouldn't steal someone's snack.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.8666661581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_02-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "こころちゃんにメッセで、譲っていいか聞いてみたら\n{user}さんのためならどうぞって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I messaged Kokoro-chan asking if I could give it to you‚\nshe said \"please go ahead if it's for {user}-san.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.7333328248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
